one;\">学生会卫生部工作报告</a></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">。我部继续秉承校学生会的优良</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://zuofengjianshezichabaogao.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">作风</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">和&ldquo;全心全意为同学服务&rdquo;的一贯宗旨，努力做好同学和</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://xuexiaogongzuojihua.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">学校</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">联系的纽带和沟通的桥梁，尽力解决同学们在生活上遇到的种种困难，为同学打造舒适的</span><u style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://xuexifangfa.unjs.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">学习</a></u><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">生活</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://baohuhuanjing.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">环境</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">。xx-x年x月份，生活部完成了新老部长的交替。通过书面</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://yubeidangyuanzhuanzheng.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">申请</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">、</span><u style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://mianshiziwojieshao.unjs.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">面试</a></u><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">等一系列过程产生了新一届部长。紧接着在x月xx日的全校学生会纳新中，生活部纳进了n位新成员，为生活部补充了新鲜血液，充实了生活部，给生活部带来了希望，迎来了生活部又一发展契机。 新一届生活部在校</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://lingdaofayangao.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">领导</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">和学生会团委的指导下，通过生活部22位成员的共同努力，在同学们的热情支持下开展了一些活动。现将生活部开展的一些活动总结如下：一.在x月xx日和xx月xx日分别进行了本学年的n次卫生检查。其中第二次的卫生检查涉及到部分</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">学院</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">n个宿舍，并且是在新的条例下，用全新的记分表进行的。x月xx日是新一届生活部的</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://diyicizuowen.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">第一次</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">宿舍卫生检查，由于处于评估前夕，因此此次检查的对象是我校大一新生和大二全部宿舍。在大一和大二全体学生的热情配合和生活部成员的积极努力下，卫生检查和公布工作圆满完成。唯一的不足就是在第二次全院学生宿舍卫生检查时，大三和大四的某些宿舍未留人，使我们无法检查。这是我们工作的失误，以后我们会尽量通知到位。二. 我们对学生宿舍卫生检查条例和学生宿舍卫生检查记分表进行了修改。鉴于原条例在实际生活操作中要求不明确，同学们不易完全按条例要求完成的缺点，我们生活部对其进行了修改。我们从实际和目的出发，将条例按卫生检查的要求进行了点的修改，以点带动面，使同学们在按照点的要求去做，在不知不觉中将宿舍卫生提高上去了，相应的宿舍检查时用的记分表也需要修改，</span>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://www.unjs.com/fanwenwang/gzbg/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">工作报告</a></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">《</span><a href=\"http://www.unjs.com/fanwenwang/gzbg/20121020000000_903134.html\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">学生会卫生部工作报告</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">》(</span><a href=\"http://www.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">http://www.unjs.com</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">)。我们在修改这项表格时，注意了主观因素对检查结果的影响，为了最大程度地给同学们以公平，我们在修改时将</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://xiangmushishifangan.unjs.com/\" style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">项目</a><span style=\"font: 14px/28px 宋体